程序包 hw3

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AbstractEvaluator
    The class AbstractEvaluator includes common code for all evaluator types.
    AllPrimesEvaluator
    Evaluator for a hand in which the rank of each card is a prime number.
    CatchAllEvaluator
    Evaluator satisfied by any set of cards.
    FourOfAKindEvaluator
    Evaluator for a hand containing (at least) four cards of the same rank.
    FullHouseEvaluator
    Evaluator for a generalized full house.
    OnePairEvaluator
    Evaluator for a hand containing (at least) two cards of the same rank.
    StraightEvaluator
    Evaluator for a hand consisting of a "straight" in which the card ranks are consecutive numbers.
    StraightFlushEvaluator
    Evaluator for a hand consisting of a "straight" in which the card ranks are consecutive numbers AND the cards all have the same suit.
    ThreeOfAKindEvaluator
    Evaluator for a hand containing (at least) three cards of the same rank.
